  "instructions": [
    "Cut beef into thin strips.",
    "Slice onion thinly and mince garlic.",
    "Finely chop red chili peppers.",
    "Mix tomato sauce, ketchup, soy sauce, rice wine vinegar in a bowl. Add milk and cream cheese, stir until smooth.",
    "Heat olive oil in a pan over medium-high heat. Stir-fry beef strips for 5 minutes or until browned.",
    "Add onion, garlic, chili peppers to the pan with beef. Cook for another minute.",
    "Pour prepared aoli sauce mixture into the pan and mix well. Simmer for an additional 2-3 minutes.",
